<br>
What I mean by a raiding guild is a guild that's main focus is raids. One that doesn't have the line 'we are not a raiding guild' in their charter.<br>
<br>
I think that a guild who doesn't consider their self a 'raiding' guild is best suited with a system that doesn't depend on the amount of raids a member goes on.<br>
<br>
